divs: Sighting DetailsWas walking my two dogs with my 15 year old son around the block. I noticed the UFO in the western sky (~45 degree agle up) and pointed it out to my son, who said it was a blimp. I told him it wasn't. I went inside my home to grab my binoculars to verify the shape of the object. After showing the object to my son, and convinced him it wasn't a blimp,I came inside to grab my digital camera with a 12x zoom. I shot these pictures at max. zoom of 12x over about 5-10 minutes. I lost site of the object behind the clouds.
